OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FThree construction firms in Jersey
OL,7,Fhave ceased trading, leaving 78 people
OL,8,Fjobless.
OL,10,FKalmac Construction, MAC Energy and
OL,11,FEden Interiors announced on Monday 22
OL,12,FJuly that they have applied for
OL,13,Finsolvency "with great disappointment
OL,14,Fand sadness".
OL,16,FThe firms say they have lost two-
OL,17,Fthirds of their work over the past
OL,18,Fyear due to the downturn in Jersey's
OL,19,Fhousing market.
