OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FSteve Jackson, Group Director for
OL,7,FJersey Government's Customer and Local
OL,8,FServices, says they can offer all
OL,9,Faffected employees and their families
OL,10,Ffree help and guidance.
OL,12,FHe explains: "Officers will ensure
OL,13,Fthat they have the support they need
OL,14,Fto understand all of the financial and
OL,15,Femployment support that will be made
OL,16,Favailable at this difficult time."
