OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FJersey Construction Council Chairman
OL,7,FAdrian De Gruchy explains: "Brexit,
OL,8,FCovid, bank interest rates and
OL,9,Fspiralling material price increases
OL,10,Fhave had a
OL,12,Flasting effect and our industry is
OL,13,Ftrying to financially manage the
OL,14,Fdelivery of affordable
OL,16,Fprojects, so as to avoid those long
OL,17,Ftroughs which a business may never
OL,18,Fclimb out of."
